casebody.data:
Dianna QUAMINA, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
STELLA GARDENS APARTMENTS, Defendant. M-688/689 September Term 2017
079309 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-688) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-689) is denied.
